## Usage

### Run Setup Script

**Linux/macOS:**
```bash
chmod +x setup-agents.sh
./setup-agents.sh
```

**Windows:**
```cmd
setup-agents.bat
```

### Using Skills

Reference skills in your prompts:
```
Use @skill-name to help me with...
```

Or use the skill command syntax:
```
>> /skill-name help me...
```

